query: Street Tacos Y Mas, Venus Texas!
name: Street Tacos Y Mas, Venus Texas!
review_text: Found this little taco truck while going for a drive and knew I had to try it. My friend and I were not hungry so we got two tacos and a churro. Believe me when I say this was one of the best tacos I’ve ever had. The steak was packed with flavor and juicy. Even the grilled onions served with had so much flavor. The churro was perfectly crispy on the outside and pillowy on the inside. We got the caramel one and loved it but I’d love to go back and get chocolate. I will 100% come back. In fact I’m going to have to limit myself on how often I come.
